description:
Danny recaps the season finale of Vanderpump Rules, which featured an iconic ending, and some other stuff before it. Plus, Randall Klein from Bravo's Camp Getaway zooms in to chat about the season, fave camp entertainment, Andrew Keegan, and more!


Camp Getaway Interview: 33ish
